## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- **Estate Math**: `cargo test` in [chronos.rs](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/chronos.rs) to verify weighted mean/SD calculation.
- **Journey**: `cargo test --test journey_tests` for end-to-end "Populist Surge" validation.
- **Command**: `cargo test --manifest-path brinkmanship_engine/Cargo.toml`

### Manual Verification
- **UI Logic**: Check `/api/state` DTO to ensure `player_ideology` contains the new derived `center` and `spread` fields.
- **Scenario parity**: Update [modern_geopolitics/scenario.json](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/scenarios/modern_geopolitics/scenario.json) to include the initial Estate definitions.
